OrganizationWorkFlow Project


Frontend: Angular 16
Features: String interpolation, two-way data binding, custom pipes.

Components: Home, Add Details (form for CRUD operations), Not Found.

Styling: Bootstrap 5 for responsive UI.
Integration: Communicates with Spring Boot backend using CORS.


Backend: Spring Boot
Entities:
Employee (Many-to-One with Country).
Country (Stores country details).

Technologies: Spring Data JPA, Lombok, MySQL for database management.

Architecture: Database → DAO → Service → Controller → Angular Frontend.

Flow Example:
A user can add or edit employee details via Angular forms,
which send requests to backend APIs to perform CRUD operations and update the database.
